var book = {
	"name": "Song of Songs",
	"numChapters": 8,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Solomon’s Song of Songs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17539A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17539A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Let him kiss me with the kisses of his mouth—for your love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17540B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17540B\"></sup> is more delightful than wine.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17540C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17540C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Pleasing is the fragrance of your perfumes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17541D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17541D\"></sup>your name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17541E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17541E\"></sup> is like perfume poured out.No wonder the young women<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17541F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17541F\"></sup> love you!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Take me away with you—let us hurry!Let the king bring me into his chambers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17542G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17542G\"></sup>We rejoice and delight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17542H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17542H\"></sup> in you;we will praise your love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17542I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17542I\"></sup> more than wine.How right they are to adore you!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Dark am I, yet lovely,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17543J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17543J\"></sup>daughters of Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17543K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17543K\"></sup>dark like the tents of Kedar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17543L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17543L\"></sup>like the tent curtains of Solomon.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Do not stare at me because I am dark,because I am darkened by the sun.My mother’s sons were angry with meand made me take care of the vineyards;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17544M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17544M\"></sup>my own vineyard I had to neglect.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Tell me, you whom I love,where you graze your flockand where you rest your sheep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17545N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17545N\"></sup> at midday.Why should I be like a veiled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17545O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17545O\"></sup> womanbeside the flocks of your friends?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>If you do not know, most beautiful of women,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17546P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17546P\"></sup>follow the tracks of the sheepand graze your young goatsby the tents of the shepherds.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I liken you, my darling, to a mareamong Pharaoh’s chariot horses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17547Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17547Q\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Your cheeks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17548R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17548R\"></sup> are beautiful with earrings,your neck with strings of jewels.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17548S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17548S\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>We will make you earrings of gold,studded with silver.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>While the king was at his table,my perfume spread its fragrance.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17550T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17550T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>My beloved is to me a sachet of myrrh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17551U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17551U\"></sup>resting between my breasts.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>My beloved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17552V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17552V\"></sup> is to me a cluster of henna<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17552W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17552W\"></sup> blossomsfrom the vineyards of En Gedi.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17552X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17552X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>How beautiful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17553Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17553Y\"></sup> you are, my darling!Oh, how beautiful!Your eyes are doves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17553Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17553Z\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>How handsome you are, my beloved!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17554AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17554AA\"></sup>Oh, how charming!And our bed is verdant.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The beams of our house are cedars;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17555AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17555AB\"></sup>our rafters are firs."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>I am a rose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17556A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17556A\"></sup> of Sharon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17556B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17556B\"></sup>a lily<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17556C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17556C\"></sup> of the valleys.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Like a lily among thornsis my darling among the young women.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Like an apple tree among the trees of the forestis my beloved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17558D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17558D\"></sup> among the young men.I delight<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17558E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17558E\"></sup> to sit in his shade,and his fruit is sweet to my taste.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17558F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17558F\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Let him lead me to the banquet hall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17559G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17559G\"></sup>and let his banner<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17559H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17559H\"></sup> over me be love.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Strengthen me with raisins,refresh me with apples,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17560I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17560I\"></sup>for I am faint with love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17560J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17560J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>His left arm is under my head,and his right arm embraces me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17561K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17561K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Daughters of Jerusalem, I charge you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17562L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17562L\"></sup>by the gazelles and by the does of the field:Do not arouse or awaken loveuntil it so desires.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17562M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17562M\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Listen! My beloved!Look! Here he comes,leaping across the mountains,bounding over the hills.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17563N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17563N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>My beloved is like a gazelle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17564O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17564O\"></sup> or a young stag.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17564P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17564P\"></sup>Look! There he stands behind our wall,gazing through the windows,peering through the lattice.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>My beloved spoke and said to me,“Arise, my darling,my beautiful one, come with me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>See! The winter is past;the rains are over and gone.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Flowers appear on the earth;the season of singing has come,the cooing of dovesis heard in our land.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The fig tree forms its early fruit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17568Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17568Q\"></sup>the blossoming<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17568R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17568R\"></sup> vines spread their fragrance.Arise, come, my darling;my beautiful one, come with me.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>My dove<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17569S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17569S\"></sup> in the clefts of the rock,in the hiding places on the mountainside,show me your face,let me hear your voice;for your voice is sweet,and your face is lovely.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17569T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17569T\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Catch for us the foxes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17570U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17570U\"></sup>the little foxesthat ruin the vineyards,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17570V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17570V\"></sup>our vineyards that are in bloom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17570W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17570W\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>My beloved is mine and I am his;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17571X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17571X\"></sup>he browses among the lilies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17571Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17571Y\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Until the day breaksand the shadows flee,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17572Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17572Z\"></sup>turn, my beloved,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17572AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17572AA\"></sup>and be like a gazelleor like a young stag<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17572AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17572AB\"></sup>on the rugged hills.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17572AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17572AC\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>All night long on my bedI looked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17573A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17573A\"></sup> for the one my heart loves;I looked for him but did not find him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will get up now and go about the city,through its streets and squares;I will search for the one my heart loves.So I looked for him but did not find him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The watchmen found meas they made their rounds in the city.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17575B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17575B\"></sup>“Have you seen the one my heart loves?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Scarcely had I passed themwhen I found the one my heart loves.I held him and would not let him gotill I had brought him to my mother’s house,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17576C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17576C\"></sup>to the room of the one who conceived me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17576D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17576D\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Daughters of Jerusalem, I charge you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17577E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17577E\"></sup>by the gazelles and by the does of the field:Do not arouse or awaken loveuntil it so desires.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17577F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17577F\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Who is this coming up from the wilderness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17578G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17578G\"></sup>like a column of smoke,perfumed with myrrh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17578H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17578H\"></sup> and incensemade from all the spices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17578I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17578I\"></sup> of the merchant?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Look! It is Solomon’s carriage,escorted by sixty warriors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17579J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17579J\"></sup>the noblest of Israel,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>all of them wearing the sword,all experienced in battle,each with his sword at his side,prepared for the terrors of the night.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17580K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17580K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>King Solomon made for himself the carriage;he made it of wood from Lebanon.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Its posts he made of silver,its base of gold.Its seat was upholstered with purple,its interior inlaid with love.Daughters of Jerusalem,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">11 </sup>come out,and look, you daughters of Zion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17583L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17583L\"></sup>Look on King Solomon wearing a crown,the crown with which his mother crowned himon the day of his wedding,the day his heart rejoiced.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17583M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17583M\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>How beautiful you are, my darling!Oh, how beautiful!Your eyes behind your veil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17584A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17584A\"></sup> are doves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17584B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17584B\"></sup>Your hair is like a flock of goatsdescending from the hills of Gilead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17584C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17584C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Your teeth are like a flock of sheep just shorn,coming up from the washing.Each has its twin;not one of them is alone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17585D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17585D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Your lips are like a scarlet ribbon;your mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17586E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17586E\"></sup> is lovely.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17586F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17586F\"></sup>Your temples behind your veilare like the halves of a pomegranate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17586G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17586G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your neck is like the tower<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17587H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17587H\"></sup> of David,built with courses of stone;on it hang a thousand shields,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17587I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17587I\"></sup>all of them shields of warriors.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Your breasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17588J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17588J\"></sup> are like two fawns,like twin fawns of a gazelle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17588K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17588K\"></sup>that browse among the lilies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17588L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17588L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Until the day breaksand the shadows flee,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17589M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17589M\"></sup>I will go to the mountain of myrrh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17589N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17589N\"></sup>and to the hill of incense.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You are altogether beautiful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17590O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17590O\"></sup> my darling;there is no flaw<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17590P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17590P\"></sup> in you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Come with me from Lebanon, my bride,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17591Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17591Q\"></sup>come with me from Lebanon.Descend from the crest of Amana,from the top of Senir,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17591R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17591R\"></sup> the summit of Hermon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17591S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17591S\"></sup>from the lions’ densand the mountain haunts of leopards.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You have stolen my heart, my sister, my bride;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17592T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17592T\"></sup>you have stolen my heartwith one glance of your eyes,with one jewel of your necklace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17592U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17592U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>How delightful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17593V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17593V\"></sup> is your love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17593W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17593W\"></sup>, my sister, my bride!How much more pleasing is your love than wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17593X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17593X\"></sup>and the fragrance of your perfume<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17593Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17593Y\"></sup>more than any spice!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Your lips drop sweetness as the honeycomb, my bride;milk and honey are under your tongue.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17594Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17594Z\"></sup>The fragrance of your garmentsis like the fragrance of Lebanon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17594AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17594AA\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You are a garden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17595AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17595AB\"></sup> locked up, my sister, my bride;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17595AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17595AC\"></sup>you are a spring enclosed, a sealed fountain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17595AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17595AD\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Your plants are an orchard of pomegranates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17596AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17596AE\"></sup>with choice fruits,with henna<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17596AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17596AF\"></sup> and nard,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>nard and saffron,calamus and cinnamon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17597AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17597AG\"></sup>with every kind of incense tree,with myrrh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17597AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17597AH\"></sup> and aloes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17597AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17597AI\"></sup>and all the finest spices.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17597AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17597AJ\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You are a garden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17598AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17598AK\"></sup> fountain,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17598AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17598AL\"></sup>a well of flowing waterstreaming down from Lebanon.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Awake, north wind,and come, south wind!Blow on my garden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17599AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17599AM\"></sup>that its fragrance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17599AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17599AN\"></sup> may spread everywhere.Let my beloved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17599AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17599AO\"></sup> come into his gardenand taste its choice fruits.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17599AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17599AP\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>I have come into my garden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17600A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17600A\"></sup> my sister, my bride;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17600B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17600B\"></sup>I have gathered my myrrh with my spice.I have eaten my honeycomb and my honey;I have drunk my wine and my milk.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17600C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17600C\"></sup>Eat, friends, and drink;drink your fill of love.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I slept but my heart was awake.Listen! My beloved is knocking:“Open to me, my sister, my darling,my dove,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17601D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17601D\"></sup> my flawless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17601E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17601E\"></sup> one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17601F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17601F\"></sup>My head is drenched with dew,my hair with the dampness of the night.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I have taken off my robe—must I put it on again?I have washed my feet—must I soil them again?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>My beloved thrust his hand through the latch-opening;my heart began to pound for him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I arose to open for my beloved,and my hands dripped with myrrh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17604G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17604G\"></sup>my fingers with flowing myrrh,on the handles of the bolt.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I opened for my beloved,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17605H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17605H\"></sup>but my beloved had left; he was gone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17605I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17605I\"></sup>My heart sank at his departure.I looked<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17605J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17605J\"></sup> for him but did not find him.I called him but he did not answer.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The watchmen found meas they made their rounds in the city.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17606K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17606K\"></sup>They beat me, they bruised me;they took away my cloak,those watchmen of the walls!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Daughters of Jerusalem, I charge you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17607L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17607L\"></sup>—if you find my beloved,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17607M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17607M\"></sup>what will you tell him?Tell him I am faint with love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17607N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17607N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>How is your beloved better than others,most beautiful of women?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17608O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17608O\"></sup>How is your beloved better than others,that you so charge us?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>My beloved is radiant and ruddy,outstanding among ten thousand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17609P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17609P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>His head is purest gold;his hair is wavyand black as a raven.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His eyes are like doves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17611Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17611Q\"></sup>by the water streams,washed in milk,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17611R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17611R\"></sup>mounted like jewels.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>His cheeks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17612S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17612S\"></sup> are like beds of spice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17612T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17612T\"></sup>yielding perfume.His lips are like lilies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17612U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17612U\"></sup>dripping with myrrh.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17612V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17612V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>His arms are rods of goldset with topaz.His body is like polished ivorydecorated with lapis lazuli.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17613W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17613W\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>His legs are pillars of marbleset on bases of pure gold.His appearance is like Lebanon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17614X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17614X\"></sup>choice as its cedars.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>His mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17615Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17615Y\"></sup> is sweetness itself;he is altogether lovely.This is my beloved,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17615Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17615Z\"></sup> this is my friend,daughters of Jerusalem.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17615AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17615AA\"></sup>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Where has your beloved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17616A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17616A\"></sup> gone,most beautiful of women?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17616B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17616B\"></sup>Which way did your beloved turn,that we may look for him with you?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>My beloved has gone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17617C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17617C\"></sup> down to his garden,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17617D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17617D\"></sup>to the beds of spices,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17617E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17617E\"></sup>to browse in the gardensand to gather lilies.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I am my beloved’s and my beloved is mine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17618F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17618F\"></sup>he browses among the lilies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17618G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17618G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>You are as beautiful as Tirzah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17619H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17619H\"></sup> my darling,as lovely as Jerusalem,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17619I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17619I\"></sup>as majestic as troops with banners.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17619J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17619J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Turn your eyes from me;they overwhelm me.Your hair is like a flock of goatsdescending from Gilead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17620K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17620K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Your teeth are like a flock of sheepcoming up from the washing.Each has its twin,not one of them is missing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17621L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17621L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your temples behind your veil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17622M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17622M\"></sup>are like the halves of a pomegranate.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17622N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17622N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Sixty queens<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17623O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17623O\"></sup> there may be,and eighty concubines,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17623P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17623P\"></sup>and virgins beyond number;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>but my dove,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17624Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17624Q\"></sup> my perfect one,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17624R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17624R\"></sup> is unique,the only daughter of her mother,the favorite of the one who bore her.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17624S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17624S\"></sup>The young women saw her and called her blessed;the queens and concubines praised her.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Who is this that appears like the dawn,fair as the moon, bright as the sun,majestic as the stars in procession?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I went down to the grove of nut treesto look at the new growth in the valley,to see if the vines had buddedor the pomegranates were in bloom.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17626T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17626T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Before I realized it,my desire set me among the royal chariots of my people.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Come back, come back, O Shulammite;come back, come back, that we may gaze on you!Why would you gaze on the Shulammiteas on the dance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17628U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17628U\"></sup> of Mahanaim?"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>How beautiful your sandaled feet,O prince’s<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17629A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17629A\"></sup> daughter!Your graceful legs are like jewels,the work of an artist’s hands.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Your navel is a rounded gobletthat never lacks blended wine.Your waist is a mound of wheatencircled by lilies.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Your breasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17631B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17631B\"></sup> are like two fawns,like twin fawns of a gazelle.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your neck is like an ivory tower.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17632C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17632C\"></sup>Your eyes are the pools of Heshbon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17632D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17632D\"></sup>by the gate of Bath Rabbim.Your nose is like the tower of Lebanon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17632E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17632E\"></sup>looking toward Damascus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Your head crowns you like Mount Carmel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17633F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17633F\"></sup>Your hair is like royal tapestry;the king is held captive by its tresses.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>How beautiful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17634G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17634G\"></sup> you are and how pleasing,my love, with your delights!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17634H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17634H\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your stature is like that of the palm,and your breasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17635I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17635I\"></sup> like clusters of fruit.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I said, “I will climb the palm tree;I will take hold of its fruit.”May your breasts be like clusters of grapes on the vine,the fragrance of your breath like apples,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17636J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17636J\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and your mouth like the best wine.May the wine go straight to my beloved,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17637K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17637K\"></sup>flowing gently over lips and teeth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I belong to my beloved,and his desire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17638L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17638L\"></sup> is for me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17638M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17638M\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Come, my beloved, let us go to the countryside,let us spend the night in the villages.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Let us go early to the vineyards<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17640N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17640N\"></sup>to see if the vines have budded,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17640O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17640O\"></sup>if their blossoms<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17640P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17640P\"></sup> have opened,and if the pomegranates<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17640Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17640Q\"></sup> are in bloom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17640R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17640R\"></sup>—there I will give you my love.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The mandrakes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17641S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17641S\"></sup> send out their fragrance,and at our door is every delicacy,both new and old,that I have stored up for you, my beloved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17641T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17641T\"></sup>"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>If only you were to me like a brother,who was nursed at my mother’s breasts!Then, if I found you outside,I would kiss you,and no one would despise me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I would lead youand bring you to my mother’s house<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17643A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17643A\"></sup>—she who has taught me.I would give you spiced wine to drink,the nectar of my pomegranates.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>His left arm is under my headand his right arm embraces me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17644B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17644B\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Daughters of Jerusalem, I charge you:Do not arouse or awaken loveuntil it so desires.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17645C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17645C\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Who is this coming up from the wilderness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17646D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17646D\"></sup>leaning on her beloved?Under the apple tree I roused you;there your mother conceived<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17646E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17646E\"></sup> you,there she who was in labor gave you birth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Place me like a seal over your heart,like a seal on your arm;for love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17647F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17647F\"></sup> is as strong as death,its jealousy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17647G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17647G\"></sup> unyielding as the grave.It burns like blazing fire,like a mighty flame.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Many waters cannot quench love;rivers cannot sweep it away.If one were to giveall the wealth of one’s house for love,it would be utterly scorned.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17648H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17648H\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>We have a little sister,and her breasts are not yet grown.What shall we do for our sisteron the day she is spoken for?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>If she is a wall,we will build towers of silver on her.If she is a door,we will enclose her with panels of cedar.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I am a wall,and my breasts are like towers.Thus I have become in his eyeslike one bringing contentment.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Solomon had a vineyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17652I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17652I\"></sup> in Baal Hamon;he let out his vineyard to tenants.Each was to bring for its fruita thousand shekels<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17652J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17652J\"></sup> of silver.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But my own vineyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17653K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17653K\"></sup> is mine to give;the thousand shekels are for you, Solomon,and two hundred are for those who tend its fruit.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You who dwell in the gardenswith friends in attendance,let me hear your voice!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Come away, my beloved,and be like a gazelle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17655L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17655L\"></sup>or like a young stag<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17655M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17655M\"></sup>on the spice-laden mountains.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-17655N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-17655N\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;